1003
00:50:38,326 --> 00:50:40,427
<i>Isn't it all kind of crazy?</i>

1004
00:50:40,429 --> 00:50:42,395
<i>All we are is curious</i>

1005
00:50:42,397 --> 00:50:44,531
<i>There's nothing wrong
