1006
00:50:44,533 --> 00:50:47,734
<i>So go 'round every corner</i>

1007
00:50:47,736 --> 00:50:49,101
You call that art?

1008
00:50:49,103 --> 00:50:51,603
<i>Search every part of the sky</i>

1009
00:50:51,605 --> 00:50:53,239
- What is he doing?
- Is he really gonna fly?

1010
00:50:53,241 --> 00:50:57,313
<i>'Cause a life
that's full of wonder</i>

1011
00:50:58,612 --> 00:51:01,183
<i>Is a wonderful life</i>

1012
00:51:32,480 --> 00:51:35,047
- Blossom, sit.
- I got you.

1013
00:51:35,049 --> 00:51:36,516
Down. Down!

1014
00:51:43,592 --> 00:51:45,224
Do you see
what you've started?

1015
00:51:45,226 --> 00:51:46,525
Yes! Do you?

1016
00:51:46,527 --> 00:51:48,127
Look at them!

1017
00:51:48,129 --> 00:51:50,195
We have been living in fear
for too long, Dad.

1018
00:51:50,197 --> 00:51:53,232
All I ever wanted to do
was keep you safe, Meechee.

1019
00:51:53,234 --> 00:51:57,103
Everything I do, I do to
protect the village. And you.

1020
00:51:57,105 --> 00:51:58,737
I don't need you
to protect me,

1021
00:51:58,739 --> 00:52:00,440
I need you to listen to me.

1022
00:52:00,442 --> 00:52:01,741
To all of us!

1023
00:52:01,743 --> 00:52:03,509
